<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.1.6">
<l>karumpār nīḷvayal kāykatirc cennelaik kaṟṟā niṟaimaṇṭit tiṉṉa</l>
<l>virumpāk kaṉṟoṉṟu koṇṭu viḷaṅkaṉi vīḻa veṟinta pirāṉē</l>
<l>curumpār meṉkuḻal kaṉṉi yoruttikkuc cūḻvalai vaittut tiriyum</l>
<l>arampā vuṉṉai yaṟintukoṇ ṭēṉuṉak kañcuva ṉammam taravē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Lord who, when all the calves and cows gathered to eat</l>
<l rend="indent">the unripe ears of red rice in the paddy field, tall [like] sugar-cane,</l>
<l>grabbed and threw a single unwelcome calf</l>
<l rend="indent">in order to fell a wood-apple fruit!</l>
<l>Trickster who placed a net to surround a virgin girl</l>
<l rend="indent">with soft curls full of bees [and] transformed [her]!</l>
<l>I have come to know you,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] I am afraid to give you [my] breast milk.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
